      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of May 27 article about war dramas (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article on May 27 about war dramas in theater and on film referred incorrectly to the outcome of the battle of Thermopylae, depicted in ''300.'' The small band of Spartans was defeated by the Persians, not the other way around.</p>
      </block>
